该节点涉及的全局状态如下：
  - bookings (read_write): Dict mapping booking_id to {resource_id, user_id, start, end, status, created_at}
  - resources (read): Dict mapping resource_id to {name, type, capacity, operating_hours}
  - availability (read_write): Dict mapping resource_id to list of {start, end, booking_id}

请说明你对每个全局变量的理解。它的数据结构是什么？读写操作分别在什么场景下发生？
